arg.name: arg 1
arg.jname: ボタン名 (日本語、省略可)

params.sqlcmd: "select " +" SYS_TYPE_VALUE.\\"NAME\\" as \\"NAME\\", " +" SYS_TYPE_VALUE.\\"VALUE\\" as \\"VALUE\\" " +"from " +" SYS_TYPE_VALUE " +"where " +" SYS_TYPE_VALUE.\\"NAME\\" = ? " +" and SYS_TYPE_VALUE.\\"VALUE\\" = ?"
"select " +" SYS_PARAMETER.\\"NAME\\" as \\"NAME\\", " +" SYS_PARAMETER.\\"VALUE\\" as \\"VALUE\\" " +"from " +" SYS_PARAMETER " +"where " +" SYS_PARAMETER.\\"NAME\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" as \\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" as \\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_EDITION\\" as \\"PS_EDITION\\" " +"from " +" M_PS " +"where " +" M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"PS_EDITION\\" = ?"

"update " +" M_PS " +"set " +" \\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"PS_EDITION\\" = ?, " +" \\"PS_UNIT_DENOMINATOR\\" = ?, " +" \\"PS_UNIT_NUMERATOR\\" = ?, " +" \\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\" = to_date(?,'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" \\"EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE\\" = to_date(?,'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" \\"PS_SPOIL\\" = ?, " +" \\"CONS_TYP\\" = ?, " +" \\"PS_LT_FLG\\" = ?, " +" \\"PS_FIXED_LT\\" = ?, " +" \\"PS_PROP_LT\\" = ?, " +" \\"PS_PROP_LOT_SIZE\\" = ?, " +" \\"PS_REF_NO\\" = ?, " +" \\"COST_UP_TYP\\" = ?, " +" \\"MRP_EXP_TYP\\" = ? " +"where " +" M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"PS_EDITION\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" as \\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" as \\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_EDITION\\" as \\"PS_EDITION\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_UNIT_DENOMINATOR\\" as \\"PS_UNIT_DENOMINATOR\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_UNIT_NUMERATOR\\" as \\"PS_UNIT_NUMERATOR\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\",'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE\\",'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_SPOIL\\" as \\"PS_SPOIL\\", " +" M_PS.\\"CONS_TYP\\" as \\"CONS_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_LT_FLG\\" as \\"PS_LT_FLG\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_FIXED_LT\\" as \\"PS_FIXED_LT\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_PROP_LT\\" as \\"PS_PROP_LT\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_PROP_LOT_SIZE\\" as \\"PS_PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_REF_NO\\" as \\"PS_REF_NO\\", " +" M_PS.\\"COST_UP_TYP\\" as \\"COST_UP_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"MRP_EXP_TYP\\" as \\"MRP_EXP_TYP\\" " +"from " +" M_PS " +"where " +" M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"PS_EDITION\\" = ?"
"delete from " +" M_PS " +"where " +" M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"PS_EDITION\\" = ?"
